---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Hunter Myers</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Tech Lead &middot; Cloud Architect &middot; Commercial Pilot &middot; Randonneur</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <p>
      Cloud and platform engineer with 10+ years translating complex system requirements into scalable infrastructure — 
      from avionics software at Garmin to geothermal energy startup Dandelion Energy to data platforms, cloud migration,
      and FinOps pipelines at Cardinal Health. My path through aerospace engineering, full stack development, and startup 
      environments gives me an unusually broad foundation for infrastructure and data work, and a track record 
      of leading technical initiatives across teams and domains.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of work I build and fly experimental aircraft — N41HM is a
      <a href="https://www.flightaware.com/live/flight/N41HM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Van's RV-7A I built myself</a>,
      and I hold a commercial pilot certificate with instrument and tailwheel ratings.
      I am also beginning a journey in the endurance cycling sport of 
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@RandoGuy-g3q" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Randonneuring</a>
      — unsupported long-distance brevets ranging from 200km to 1200km.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site runs on a Kubernetes cluster I manage at home, served by nginx in a container,
      deployed via Helm, and routed through Traefik. The same cluster runs a
      rain barrel irrigation system I built end-to-end: custom IoT hardware, MQTT,
      a Django webapp, and a PostgreSQL database — all on bare metal in my basement.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Aviation</h3>
        <p>Commercial pilot, instrument rated, tailwheel endorsed. Built and fly a Van's RV-7A (N41HM). B.S. Aerospace Engineering.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Randonneuring</h3>
        <p>Endurance and ultra-endurance unsupported cycling on a recumbent. Working towards a 200km gravel brevet and documenting the journey on YouTube.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Home Infrastructure</h3>
        <p>Bare-metal k8s cluster, Helm, Traefik, custom IoT devices, MQTT, and a rain barrel automation system built from scratch.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
